snippet.title: Super Mario Defence (Mario Flash Game) Gameplay
snippet.description:
Mario & Luigi clones are coming to stop Bowser Stop them all
Bowser build DUPLICON 3000 but suddenly it was sent to pipe by accident
they've found out the machine and try to use it they're doing more clones
Bowser must stop them before they get to the castle use his army to get rid of them
